{"tid":2126782,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"重溫下搣時潘個臭西既on9舊post - 偷睇男朋友電話睇到喊","createTime":"2020-07-27T04:51:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T08:54:08.000Z","uid":118628,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7893bb3847c47762c952e81ad8aad7f6873704ee","tid":2126782,"uid":118628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T04:51:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拍拖一年，趁男朋友訓著，偷睇佢電話睇吓有冇通姦證據。點知俾我睇到佢同幾個fd講打算同我結婚，仲有好多次fd約佢佢都推咗話要陪女朋友......搞到我好感動。<br />\n<br />\n之前我返工佢讀碩士，佢每日都陪我搭車入屯門/天水圍送我返工，再搭返車出沙田，我放工佢成日話嚟唔到接我，但一出公司就會見到佢，帶埋飯俾我食。<br />\n<br />\n我知你有上連登，好多時我把口冇講，但我知你對我好好，我哋一齊努力儲錢結婚啦。我愛你。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/30/062107_5cc8564edcbf7a3b0fdb0e86dd96ba89.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F30%2F062107_5cc8564edcbf7a3b0fdb0e86dd96ba89.png&h=8683f26f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/30/062109_d11c262292bdc3ae464bcf67529ab7a7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F30%2F062109_d11c262292bdc3ae464bcf67529ab7a7.png&h=286a84e0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/30/062111_b68844d65f37c047b56907f163d2ac96.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F30%2F062111_b68844d65f37c047b56907f163d2ac96.png&h=0ac68aaa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/30/062113_20625f34c5d6186fa5399b26f02a7fd5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F30%2F062113_20625f34c5d6186fa5399b26f02a7fd5.png&h=25ee64c5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"084a5b9ec9e801b8f96a59cc1b333ab1dff90bb2","tid":2126782,"uid":118628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T04:52:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/683581/page/1\" d